  (@custom "contractspecv0" (after data) "\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\1eExecutes a function call on another contract.\0a\0aRequires authentication from the account itself.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a\0a* `target` - The address of the contract to call\0a* `target_fn` - The function name to call on the target contract\0a* `target_args` - The arguments to pass to the target function\00\00\00\00\00\07execute\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06target\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\09target_fn\00\00\00\00\00\00\11\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0btarget_args\00\00\00\03\ea\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07upgrade\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0dnew_wasm_hash\00\00\00\00\00\03\ee\00\00\00 \00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\90Returns `Some(Address)` if ownership is set, or `None` if ownership has\0abeen renounced.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a\0a* `e` - Access to the Soroban environment.\00\00\00\09get_owner\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e8\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00[Adds a policy contract to a context rule.\0a\0aRequires authentication from the account itself.\00\00\00\00\0aadd_policy\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0fcontext_rule_id\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06policy\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0dinstall_param\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\00VAdds a new signer to a context rule.\0a\0aRequires authentication from the account itself.\00\00\00\00\00\0aadd_signer\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0fcontext_rule_id\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06signer\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\06Signer\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\c3Validates signatures against the account's context rules.\0a\0aVerifies that the provided signatures match the required signers for the given execution context.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a\0a* `signature_payload` - The hash of the transaction data to verify\0a* `signatures` - The signatures to validate\0a* `auth_contexts` - The execution contexts for w